channel.title: 742 Rage-Scape Issues
channel.description:
Everytime I try to compile, I get like a billion errors!, Not necessarily a billion but atleast 93 from the start.
Newly fresh, downloaded. and Extracted, set up to a vps, etc.
It just instantly gives you 93 errors when you try to "compile server".
Any fixes, help, or any "fixed" sources out there?
Any help would be appreciated.
*EDIT* I do indeed have everything set up. The JDK, setup, the Revision build etc...
Incase you need to know, I'm using "Matrix 718 Client."
(Named: 718+ Client)
